{"tid":1798810,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"關於滲透狗隊","createTime":"2019-12-26T13:23:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T21:45:52.000Z","uid":202296,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f4b419822617ae048c04b00b7487ee2bafc0740d","tid":1798810,"uid":202296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:23:49.000Z","msg":"事實:依家根本冇可能旨意狗隊變節<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n長遠嚟講，我地真係需要人滲透狗隊，好處太多，大家都諗到，所以我會講下方法，我覺得我個方法好難實行，但都希望拋磚引玉，大家一齊brainstorm下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先，滲透狗隊絕對冇可能你話一個人去考，考完就做白警咁樣，因為你如果冇強大意志力/心理質素嗰話，分分鐘未出camp已經比人洗咗腦，例子可見2014有大量黃絲入去話做白警(結果係點大家都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n然後我今日突然諗到，如果有team人可以管理呢班想做白警既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(前提係呢team人可信[亦係呢個方法最大既難處])。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 我下面講既野都係base on呢team人係可信既:<br />\n<br />\n想滲透狗隊既手足如果遴選成功嗰話，交低資料比呢team人，好似老豆搵仔嗰啲咁，萬一邊日變節投靠狗隊嗰話，個人資料就會即刻被爆曬出嚟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後，我當呢team人有5個admin，呢條滲透名單就會分開5 parts，冇一個admin可以掌握曬所有滲透既手足。然後，admin會將滲透手足以3-4人分組，可能睇入學堂既時間，咁同team手足就可以互相鼓勵/監察/提醒，萬一有人變節，可以即時通知admin。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而1 team既滲透手足係除咗自己team之外唔會知道其他滲透手足身份，減少被篤灰既損失。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，其實我都係拋磚引玉架咋，根本問題都係未想到方法解決，不過滲透狗隊成效真係可以好大，歡迎大家一齊嚟brainstorm<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者可以探討下點樣直接分化狗隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"275ec5e184a652ab3102fca6bca199713634c740","tid":1798810,"uid":179292,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:25:50.000Z","msg":"滲透狗隊，2014年好多人講，你點睇"},{"pid":"e3d65b3ccb6fe6cf87405a9f498f6b9dec0f8d02","tid":1798810,"uid":15605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"275ec5e184a652ab3102fca6bca199713634c740","tid":1798810,"uid":179292,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:25:50.000Z","msg":"滲透狗隊，2014年好多人講，你點睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:28:17.000Z","msg":"出曬黎打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea056cc04e448f2b1b44def6374b6cc84bab6d40","tid":1798810,"uid":44870,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:29:28.000Z","msg":"太睇得起自己, 太睇少狗隊洗腦<br />\n2014 前車可鑑"},{"pid":"1e859e743d4362c39ebba9ee3fcf8d709168eca8","tid":1798810,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:29:47.000Z","msg":"爆個人資料有幾大阻嚇力？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3dffa3c60edf61c6dced642ee9678fb976931ff","tid":1798810,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:30:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/andy-now_7GPDN_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fandy-now_7GPDN_1200x0.png&h=9a112eab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我嘅理解係<br />\n未到最後行動嗰一秒鐘<br />\n自己都未必肯定到自己企邊一面"},{"pid":"9a6d9b2242558970210b941c1946cead3d74f678","tid":1798810,"uid":131767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"275ec5e184a652ab3102fca6bca199713634c740","tid":1798810,"uid":179292,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:25:50.000Z","msg":"滲透狗隊，2014年好多人講，你點睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:30:54.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山<br />\n各有各做"},{"pid":"26b09ce815110715775b60fbf7e0bf4958b9b7c9","tid":1798810,"uid":1122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:31:25.000Z","msg":"同team人都要唔可以見面，所有野都要經admin去處理會更加保障"},{"pid":"3f3b81c976948e9858ddeaffec333c11819b12f0","tid":1798810,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:31:32.000Z","msg":"Facebook洗地組正式成立！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1798781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1798781</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"54b4a5695296177ad301b355015a6d5b3cf21f71","tid":1798810,"uid":248290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:31:57.000Z","msg":"無間道&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44950c7a40b0b5eccef5ead6ecc5ba56a1c4a788","tid":1798810,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:35:08.000Z","msg":"黃到金既唔會變節,但狗隊一查就知你係黃唔俾入<br />\n唔係黃到金既,過到狗既審查,變節既機會....<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ccd0e88ae8f97959735a3dfc762baa77ee3d0c","tid":1798810,"uid":295442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T14:07:48.000Z","msg":"唔係去考！係用現貨變黃金！重量級！"},{"pid":"8e3fec457dd516d6e6e48f72a07dc1233d455b6e","tid":1798810,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3d65b3ccb6fe6cf87405a9f498f6b9dec0f8d02","tid":1798810,"uid":15605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"275ec5e184a652ab3102fca6bca199713634c740","tid":1798810,"uid":179292,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:25:50.000Z","msg":"滲透狗隊，2014年好多人講，你點睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:28:17.000Z","msg":"出曬黎打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T19:02:16.000Z","msg":"做前鋒打手足、拉小朋友、強姦女人、毁屍滅跡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4afd37fcb53a9bdc5323aa4828db62e997041ef","tid":1798810,"uid":302140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T19:04:59.000Z","msg":"入到去唔變節一樣好難改變到d咩。"},{"pid":"1906e84358654cc67a8863d3604b8f32fdb3e501","tid":1798810,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"275ec5e184a652ab3102fca6bca199713634c740","tid